pty \r\nstring\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:765:                                skips the STYLE block entirely.\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:766:      outline_spine             one-line-per-beat compact rendering\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:767:                                of the whole outline so the \r\ncomposer\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:768:                                can see the arc it is participating\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:769:                                in. Empty string skips the OUTLINE\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:770:                                block entirely. Renderer ships in \r\nthis\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:771:                                module (`render_outline_spine`).\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:772:      character_voice_card      one-line `name (gender, traits)` \r\nblurb\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:773:                                for the speaker of this beat. Empty\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:774:                                string skips the CHARACTER block. \r\nBuilt\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:775:                                from cast_rows via \r\n`build_voice_card`.\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:776:\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:777:    Prompt placement is static-first / variable-second (style +\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:778:    canon_header + outline_spine + allowed_roster are stable across\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:779:    every composer call in the episode; voice_card + last_lines +\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:780:    speaker + intent change per call). Once KV-cache reuse lands in\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_