no hedge phrase. \r\nBoth new\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3486:    params default \"\" so legacy callers/tests are byte-identical.\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3487:\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3488:    `creative_repo_id` is accepted for call-signature parity with\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3489:    `compose_line` (see `compose_announcer_intro`).\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3490:\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3491:    Returns a `LineResult`; `compose_flags` is \r\n``(\"announcer_outro\",)``\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3492:    on the LLM path or ``(\"announcer_outro_fallback\",)`` on \r\nfallback.\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3493:    \"\"\"\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3494:    try:\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3504:\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3505:    resolved = is_resolved_ending_change(ending_change)\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3506:    ending = clean_one_line(ending_change or \"\", max_chars=240)\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3507:    final_line = clean_one_line(final_character_line or \"\", \r\nmax_chars=240)\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3508:\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3509:    # LLM slot: creative -- announcer outro is a narrative framing\r\n  production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3510:    # pass; routed through the writer's creative_writing_model \r\nslot.\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3511:    brief = clean_one_line(script_brief or \"\", max_chars=0)\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3512:    close = clean_one_line(news_close_brief or \"\", max_chars=0)\r\n> production_mirror\\nodes\\_otr_line_composer.py:3513:    intro = clean_one_line(intro_